bio:
During my study business economics I noticed that I really got excited from the several financial problem statements we had to solve during our projects. 

The whole process from the internal and external analysis of the company to the final recommendations and translation in financial numbers interested me from the beginning. I appreciate the challenge of solving these problems and giving recommendations.
